# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Contact form backend (Web3Forms)
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# The /reservation contact form POSTs to https://api.web3forms.com
# and delivers submissions to BUSINESS.email
# (japanesedetailergirl@gmail.com). To enable silent in-page
# submission (no mailer pop-up), set this access key:
#
#   1. Go to https://web3forms.com/
#   2. Enter japanesedetailergirl@gmail.com under "Your Email"
#   3. Web3Forms emails an access key to that address — copy it
#   4. Paste the key below (and into Vercel Project Settings →
#      Environment Variables) and redeploy
#
# The key is safe to expose client-side: rate-limit + domain-allow
# is enforced on the Web3Forms dashboard. If this variable is
# unset, the form falls back to showing a mailto: link so visitors
# can always get through.
NEXT_PUBLIC_WEB3FORMS_ACCESS_KEY=
